{"tid":2422184,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 艾利臣老豆係巴西潛水時遇溺死亡","createTime":"2021-02-25T04:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T16:03:15.000Z","uid":73381,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"451634ed7da1c8af547afc11c209d536f60e5129","tid":2422184,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:26:29.000Z","msg":"Father of Liverpool goalkeeper Alisson drowns in Brazil<br />\n<br />\n(Reuters) - The father of Liverpool goalkeeper Alisson Becker drowned in a lake near his holiday home in southern Brazil on Wednesday, local police said.<br />\n<br />\nJose Becker, 57, had been swimming at a dam on his property when the accident happened on Wednesday afternoon, Doroteo Machado Filho, a police inspector in the town of Lavras do Sul, told Reuters. No foul play was suspected.<br />\n<br />\nAlisson joined Liverpool in 2018 from Roma and was voted FIFA Best Men's Goalkeeper in 2019. His younger brother Muriel is a goalkeeper for Brazilian side Fluminense.<br />\n<br />\nInternacional, who both brothers played for, tweeted their condolences.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;It is with great sadness that we received the news of Jose Agostinho Becker's death, the father of our ex-goalkeepers Alisson and Muriel,&quot; the club said.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://uk.sports.yahoo.com/news/father-liverpool-goalkeeper-alisson-drowns-040959951.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuk.sports.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Ffather-liverpool-goalkeeper-alisson-drowns-040959951.html&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFbtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=6e8c2492\" target=\"_blank\">https://uk.sports.yahoo.com/news/father-liverpool-goalkeeper-alisson-drowns-040959951.html</a>"},{"pid":"45c22af34482a988b4193c8d75f94d07bacdbd91","tid":2422184,"uid":50745,"like":43,"dislike":4,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"利迷既詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a81767e91d3fe40a0db1e34